pan class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215270/extras/06f35de946399a4644d32850adc5e8ed.poster.avif?t=1729107435\" width=600 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215270/extras/06f35de946399a4644d32850adc5e8ed.webm?t=1729107435\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215270/extras/06f35de946399a4644d32850adc5e8ed.mp4?t=1729107435\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While playing stay watchful for a team of rogue assets seek to erase you from the game files, your journey will be anything but easy.</p>",
